*   ## **_KATSUYURI SHIBATA DEF LEE MORIARTY_**
    

Pretty great match for technical wrestling fans. Probably a bit too technical for the crowd in Kentucky on this night. Hook comes out after the match to save Shibata from a beat down

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/29e44f7d-1db5-4d87-ad3e-5a0c2b81319a/20240413_174724.jpg)

