*   ## **_DANIEL GARCIA DEF. ANGELICO_**
    

Pretty fun match but almost devoid of any heat/interest from the crowd. Pretty much the case for everything tonight

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0222874a-4fa6-4f57-943b-a41b2e2edfb5/Screenshot_20240413_180928.jpg)

*   ## **_TONI STORM(w MARIAH MAY) def. AZM(w ANNA JAY)_**
    

Excellent match. AZM came to show what she can do and Toni Storm was the perfect person to do it with.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/48633ee9-838e-41ae-bb4b-2fdfd354bba6/Screenshot_20240413_183428.jpg)

Thunder Rosa cuts a passionate promo about what she’s done to overcome adversity. She says Toni Storm wiped the make up off Rosa's face but nobody is ready for what’s underneath.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2bdf27b8-2daa-4925-bc51-499d6bc7661e/Screenshot_20240413_183401.jpg)

*   ## **_BRYAN DANIELSON AND CLAUDIO CASTAGNOLI def HOBBS AND KYLE FLETCHER_**
    

Top notch PPV Quality main event. Went more than 20 minutes. Check it out. Takeshita attacks after the match and takes Bryan out with a Brainbuster on the ramp